                    SevMerge는 IT 분야 의뢰인과 전문가를 연결하는 중개 플랫폼입니다.<br>
                    실제 작업 진행 및 계약은 전문가와 직접 협의해 주세요.
                </p>

                <div class="footer-policy-links">
                    <a href="/policys/terms">이용약관</a>
                    <a href="/policys/privacy" class="footer-policy-strong">개인정보처리방침</a>
                    <a href="/policys/ad">광고약관</a>
                    <a href="/policys/operation">운영정책</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-columns">
                <div class="footer-column">
                    <h4 class="footer-title footer-toggle">SevMerge 소개</h4>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                        <li><a href="/supports?tab=about">회사소개</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/supports?tab=careers">인재채용</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/supports?tab=partnership">제휴 문의</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="footer-column">
                    <h4 class="footer-title footer-toggle">의뢰인 안내</h4>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="footer-column">
                    <h4 class="footer-title footer-toggle">전문가 안내</h4>
                    <ul class="footer-links">

                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="footer-column">
                    <h4 class="footer-title footer-toggle">고객 지원</h4>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                        <li><a href="/boards?boardType=NOTICE">공지게시판</a></li>
